{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"ae7568c9-4d5f-4eb1-96c2-e202403e3a32","content":"Here are the five .NET 10 breaking changes you're hitting:\n\n**1. `[InlineArray]` + explicit `StructLayout(Size=…)`**\n.NET 10 now computes InlineArray layout automatically. An explicit `Size` in `StructLayout` conflicts and will throw `TypeLoadException` at runtime. **Fix:** Remove the `[StructLayout(LayoutKind.Explicit, Size = 64)]` attribute entirely—the runtime infers the correct size from the element type × length.\n\n**2. `DriveInfo.DriveFormat` on Linux**\nThe returned strings have changed in .NET 10 (now sourced differently). Any `==` comparisons against hardcoded format strings may silently stop matching. **Fix:** Verify the new values on your target OS and update comparisons, or switch to case-insensitive/contains checks where appropriate.\n\n**3. NU1510 — pruned package references**\n.NET 10 SDK enables **package reference pruning** by default, removing unused transitive references at restore. NU1510 warns about pruned packages. **Fix:** Either add explicit `<PackageReference>` entries for any transitives you actually use, or disable pruning:\n```xml\n<PropertyGroup>\n  <PrunePackageReferences>false</PrunePackageReferences>\n</PropertyGroup>\n```\n\n**4. Transitive NuGet audit warnings**\n.NET 10 changes `NuGetAuditMode` default from `direct` → `all`, so transitive vulnerabilities now surface. **Fix:** Update vulnerable transitive packages (preferred), pin safe versions, or set `<NuGetAuditMode>direct</NuGetAuditMode>` to restore old behavior.\n\n**5. `FilePatternMatch.Stem` null check**\n`Stem` is no longer nullable in .NET 10—it returns `string.Empty` instead of `null`. Your `Stem == null` check will never be true. **Fix:** Change to:\n```csharp\nstring.IsNullOrEmpty(match.Stem)\n```","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"bdb3e682-4c22-48a0-b74c-3e88d8cbc73e","outputTokens":490,"requestId":"A450:20684E:711FA84:79829A5:6A03D124"},"id":"3ccfdaad-b05d-43ea-9fa7-a4d8b5e572c0","timestamp":"2026-05-13T01:17:35.432Z","parentId":"24e329ae-e74b-4a23-b657-063a5fd902f7"}
